Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆 就拜托你看家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心理作用么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 爱 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 上来吧 上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 那副眼镜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前邮购买的灵异眼镜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 爱看上去身上有红色的光环啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗 我看上去像是有蓝色的光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是心理作用…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把精神集中就可以看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见吧 看见吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没有变啊 这对母女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 妈妈 最近遥身边发生了很多不可思议的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想调查其中的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近有买了占卜的盘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 她在担心我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是招UFO的仪式就饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是威加盘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类似西洋的狐狗狸一样的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐狗狸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 把手放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 把精神统一 不要吓到精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要温柔的温柔的祈祷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵大人 遥现在正为不可思议的事情烦恼着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我们其中的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起来祈祷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也要？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 大家要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵大人 精灵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在遥正因为不可思议的事情而烦恼着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我们其中的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵大人 精灵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是NOEIN吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事情就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得有这样的机会 来占卜更加好玩的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 来占卜下美保什么时候结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那样太难为情了 太难为情了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没有什么关系 占卜么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:05:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 结婚什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保 流鼻血了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流下来了 流下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经确认燕雀他们的座标了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 好像还没有的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些监察者都在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没有办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们杀了一个监察官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吊死的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是龙骑兵的耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀他们大概是以龙之转矩为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该在那个座标上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我先走 和鸦一起去找燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一切都混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 美保
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Byebye
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是些好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我交朋友可是好好的挑过的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀念吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个遥不是我们所知道的那个遥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为我们存在所准备的祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去想了 一切都是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里发生的一切事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀他们单独的转移到了这个时空
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙的座标不稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意一点 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真加油啊 内田 要不要喝啤酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微悠闲一下不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郡山先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的日程已经安排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请回自己的房间里去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到明天为止必须要整理资料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郡山先生难道就不在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个砖墙上的孔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样复杂的事情 应该由绝临的内田来做么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是专家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郡山先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能停止那奇怪的说话省略法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道就不能好好称呼绝对临界组织计划委员会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 内田是绝临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会告你性骚扰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经这个时间了 差不多要准备做晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:09:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃什么 汉堡包怎么样 还是奶油菜汤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的事情我是最清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以佑 好好听妈妈的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你 不要背叛妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是好孩子不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做到的 你的话一定能像姐姐一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要发呆 快练习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦 我在做想像练习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样可忍受不了了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:09:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机也不通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就被阿姨没收了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 考试什么的 就算考上好的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来变成什么样子也清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 长谷部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是你不想学习的借口罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 我是在说佑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊 长谷部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我振作点啊 男子部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情都没有 鸢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切断通道的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这里好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空是蓝色的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里消失 我也是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交喙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:11:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会那么简单就消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到龙之转矩消失为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有那样的 那个阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才去了佑的家里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（佑现在在学习中 不能玩耍 佑的妈妈）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通人会做到那种程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要考试也没有办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这可是我们在一起的最后一个暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他合格的话就要去东京了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去东京了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤真的想去东京的初中上学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 还是去见佑确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 晚上偷偷潜入佑的家里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽会对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要小心啊 你现在非常危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说我的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊 爱 不就在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座标固定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5 4 3 2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏离了 时间偏离了 偏离了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 救我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时空扭曲了么 燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 遥消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止都没有的强烈反应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就这样直走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了要直走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 是转弯的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻觉 一切都是幻觉 龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸢 解放龙之转矩的灵子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 怎么了鸢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量使用过度了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交喙 你来做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只要消灭龙之转矩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们准备把龙之转矩怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 那是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩如果存在于拉库利玛时空界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时空有消失的危险性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险 你说危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为为了让所有秩序安定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量子存在的我们拉库利玛的人民\N到了现在是在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果龙之转矩能够消灭所有时空的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就消灭好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你准备怎么办 交喙 那家伙可准备干了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气干掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始战斗了 燕雀这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交喙 快点消灭龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放…放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点干 交喙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥总有一天要消失 从你的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…住手 交喙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 数值又上升了 在这里面深处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦这家伙 引起了High side
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}高侧反冲 High side:指机车赛中因为抓地力从打滑状态 瞬间回复抓地力时的反冲 致使骑士自车体上方被甩出的意外事故
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:18:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下又没到手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.21,0:19:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 把这家伙忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 永别了 这样我也能变的轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色的…雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失…一切都给我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要毁了我们的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…大家会悲伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 想像未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己期望的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信你所拥有的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后想像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替换了不同的时空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有控制时空的力量吗 这个遥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 力气没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是 龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这异常的力量是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了交喙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会交出龙之转矩的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会把遥交出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点把他带回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了吗 刚才的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是谁相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.85,0:21:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来拍到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.37,0:21:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 怎么了 我进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.17,0:22:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不接啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须要保护这个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.56,0:22:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把鸦强制转移
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.54,0:22:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
